value.string: Ocean front at its best for whale watching and views of the Island of Molokai. Quiet location at the end of the cul de sac. Near Pool and within walking distance to Kapalua Bay Beach. 3 pools and two tennis courts for further enhancing the Bay Villa life style experience. Great location. Nice conservation area in front with path to the rocks below where the turtles come in to feed. Great ocean view.

You will love the stunning ocean views from this great Kapalua oceanfront 2 bedroom, 3 bathroom condominium. Location, location, location. This precious single level property has arguably the best location at the Kapalua Bay Villas. Extremely popular vacation rental unit. Come see for yourself and you'll see why. Comfort at a higher level, it's a perfect home to relax and enjoy the best Kapalua Resort has to offer.

Offering one of the finest 2-bedroom, 3-bathroom properties in the Kapalua Bay Villas, this property is one of the reasons why YOU keep coming back to Maui! This 1,529 square foot property was fully renovated by Maui's own Koliana Designs. Words failed to describe its beauty and location. Sold fully furnished and turn-key. Kapalua Bay Villas is an oceanfront condominium community of 141 apartments in twenty-seven 1-story and 2-story buildings. The community is spread across 16.451 acres and offers pools & tennis court. Beach front access to Kapalua Bay and Oneloa Bay is within walking distance from this oceanfront condominium community. YOUR Time is Now.

Great ocean views for whale watching and all the ocean view all day long. Near pool and easy walk to Oneloa Beach or Kapalua beach. 2 tennis courts 3 pools and barbeque areas. Outside lanai has been enclosed for greater living area for a more great room effect. The kitchen was remodelled and all opened up to the living /dining area. This unit is in private rental but easy to show when not rented. It is ready to move into and the owners have maintained the unit. Virtual tour at http://fusion.realtourvision.com/idx/31930

EXTRAORDINARY. MAUI. Enjoy stunning ocean views as well as views of the Plantation and Bay Courses from this townhouse floor plan. One of the most desirable floor plans, the townhouse style one bedroom offers views from the living area and kitchen, as well as the bedroom upstairs. The living room has been extended as has the loft upstairs, creating a larger interior and more privacy. Renovated in 2002, this property has been lovingly used and cared for as a second home and has not been in a vacation rental. Offered furnished and turnkey.

Fabulous Bridge Level unit with excellent ocean views. This is one of the rare, most desirable, upstairs, single-level floor plans. This unit has no stairs since you access from road level to a single level unit. Highly upgraded, air conditioned and offered turn-key.

This is a must see oceanfront unit with fantastic ocean views. Watch the whales and the dolphins and all the cruise ships go by. Oneloa Beach is steps away. Pool is steps away. Bridge level for easy convenient access. Unit has a great bathroom with tub and also a separate shower and also a water feature that is turned off during rentals. Kitchen and all has been upgraded also with all new cabinets and granite counter tops. Appliances were all new. Bay villas have 3 pools, near Kapalua beach, have their own tennis courts and office. Great oceanfront beachwalk for your daily exercise. Kapalua has restaurants and a spa as well as tennis and golf managed by Troon.

Proudly offering one of the finest one bedroom, two bath townhouse style condos on the "bridge level" at the Kapalua Bay Villas. This supremely upgraded condo has been completely renovated featuring a top of the line kitchen, new cabinetry, granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. Capturing incredible ocean views from the living room, bedroom and both balcony "lanais". This beautifully furnished condo features central air-conditioning, an expanded bedroom area, with all the comforts one would expect from this "Gold" quality unit in the Kapalua Villas rental program.

Oversized 1200 square foot one-bedroom oceanfront Bay Villa with terrific ocean views. This large townhouse end-unit has 2 full baths and an upstairs bedroom with panoramic views and excellent privacy. This is a must-see for your value conscious buyers.

Welcome to Kapalua Bay Villas Unit 12B 1&2 , nestled in one of the most sought after locations in Kapalua. The views from this spacious 2 bedroom and 3 full bath unit are simply breathtaking! Relax on your large covered lanai and be serenaded by the sounds of breaking waves from the world renowned white sand beach below. Grand windows encompass the majestic views of the neighboring islands of Molokai and Lanai. This impressive unit has vaulted ceilings in the living area with an upgraded floor plan allowing for a "Great Room" like atmosphere. Unit 12B 1&2 is being offered fully furnished with impeccable thought into layout and design. This unit is a fantastic vacation rental property with a proven track record. Situated on grounds that are manicured to perfection, 3 swimming pools, tennis courts, and easy access to top beaches and dining. Call now for a private showing. Its time to make your dream of owning on Maui a reality!

Ocean front living at its best. Oneloa Beach below and steps are right there below the unit. Whale watching in the winter is the very best and they feel so close at times. Molokai Island is changing colors all day long as the sun shines on it and you feel like you could paint it right then at times. Kapalua beach walk is right below you from Ironwoods to Merrimans restaurant. 3 pools on property, with the nearest pool right above parking for building 19. 2 tennis courts and office a short walk from unit. Nice walk to Kapalua beach or you can take the shuttle. Unit has been upgraded for the gold rental program. This is one level two bedroom on the Bridge or street level which makes for easy access. Unit is in private rental program. Sold Furnished. All artwork is excluded in sale.

Beautifully renovated, this stunning two-story villa is offered turn-key and fully furnished. Enjoy sweeping views of the ocean from the living room, dining, room, both bedrooms. The loft area has been enclosed to create a spacious ocean view master suite. The Bay Villas amenities include direct beach access to Oneloa Bay, three swimming pools, and two tennis courts. Centrally located in the Kapalua Resort, the Bay Villas are close to walking trails, the Spa Montage, Golf, Tennis and Dining.

You can't get much closer to the ocean than this! Stunning ocean views from this single level 1 bedroom, 1 bath Bay Villa Unit. Easy access with no steps and private bridge level entrance, the location of building 30 sits off the roadway going through the Bay Villas and provides for a quite and private master bedroom setting. The living room, dinning area and kitchen offer amazing ocean vistas. The kitchen has been enhanced with granite counter tops and the unit is bright and airy throughout. Great location for easy access to one of the many pools located in The Bay Villas, and easy walking distance to Oneloa Bay Beach and Kapalua Bay Beach, Montage Spa, the Kapalua Resort coastal trail, on site tennis courts, office and a variety of restaurants and other amenities throughout the Resort.

The Coconut Grove residences with their spacious lanais bring indoors the gentle splendor of the surrounding environment and captures the understated elegance of Kapalua. Only thirty-six residences on twelve acres fronted by coconut palms planted a hundred years ago grace this special cove called Kapalua Bay. This upstairs residence has a private ground floor entry featuring an interior stairway and elevator. There is a second entrance from the attached garage into the downstairs foyer. Residence finishings include granite kitchen counter tops, top of the line appliances, marble baths, and stone flooring. On-site amenities feature a tension-edged lap pool, whirlpool spa, exercise room, cabana with kitchen and barbeque facilities. Here you will reside in one of the loveliest places on earth.

Introducing Montage Residences Kapalua Bay. A truly one-of-a-kind opportunity to own along the West Maui shoreline, overlooking the white sandy crescent of Kapalua Bay, with panoramic ocean views framed by the neighboring islands of Molokai and Lanai. Located within the renowned Kapalua Resort, home to two championship golf courses, miles of hiking trails and an array of ocean activities. Montage Residences Kapalua Bay offers a rare opportunity to fully embrace the Montage lifestyle. The combination of unparalleled location, expansive floor plans and Montage services make for true hassle free resort living.

Prime oceanfront location in The Bay Villas. Highly desirable corner town-home style unit beautifully upgraded in 2008. Casually elegant with modern Balinese and Asian interiors. Second full bath on ground floor. Well located close to pool / BBQ area. Walk out onto a spacious lawn and only a short walk to either Kapalua Bay or Oneloa Bay. All Kapalua Resort amenities included.
